name: SYMPHONIUM I - OP IV
description: SYMPHONIUM I is an audiovisual symphony NFT in 10 parts. Each part (referred to as an Op) comprises a different layer of the SYMPHONIUM.Each Op is then run through multiple algorithms in Processing to create a digital 3d print of the sound - a sonic fingerprint if you will.Only when the full collection of 10 NFTs are played in unison can the work be experienced as it was originally intended. twitter.com/YULYSSSES
